{
  "id": "adv_card_kkr_02_01",
  "title": "赤崎こころ 1話 研究中のアイドルさん",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_lesson-00-000-noon",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――長瀬麻奈バースデーライブから数日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—A few days after the birthday live for Mana Nagase",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3033.3333333333303,
          "startTime": 3.03333333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_01-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "ここは……こう！\nいや、ちょっとタイミングが早かった？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Like this… hah!\nHmmm‚ did I time that a little too fast?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_01-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "むぅっ、今のはタイミングは合ってても\nカッコよくはありませんね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmph! Even if I got the timing right‚\nthat wouldn’t have been all that cool.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_01-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "力強くかつ、丁寧に華麗に……とうっ！\nはぁ、はぁ、今の感じは――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "More power! More elegance! Haah!\n*huff* *huff* That felt good.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.666666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "うん、いいと思うぞ\n頑張ってるな、こころ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. You’re in the groove now.\nYou’re working hard‚ Kokoro.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.666666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_01-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様です。今日はおヒマなんですか？\nこんな所で油売って～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hello. Don’t you have anything better to do?\nBut just wasting time here?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.86666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "違う……。みんなの調子を見守るのも\nマネージャーの仕事のうちだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m not wasting time. Watching everyone’s\nprogress is also part of a manager's job.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.833333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_01-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "そんなこと言って、わざわざこころが\n一人の時に来てるじゃないですか～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You say that‚ but it’s strange you turn up\nwhen I’m alone like this!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.86666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_01-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱりこころに夢中なんですか～？\nダメですよ、こころはみんなのアイドルですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You have a thing for Kokoro‚ don’t you?\nGive it up. I’m everyone’s idol!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.733333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "褒めたとたんに、これか……\nこころは相変わらずだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I compliment you‚ and look what happens.\nYou’re consistent‚ Kokoro.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_01-kkr007.m4a",
      "text": "なんですか、その言い方～\nこころがちっとも成長してないみたいじゃないですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey! What’s that supposed to mean~?\nIt almost sounds like you don’t think I’m making progress.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.63333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "いや、そんなことはないよ\nなんていうか……以前より工夫してる感じがする",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nope‚ I didn’t mean it like that.\nYou do seem to be more… thought than before.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_01-kkr008.m4a",
      "text": "なかなか鋭いですね～\n確かに今は研究中のアイドルさんがいますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You do have a good eye!\nThere is an idol I’m currently studying intently.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.13333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_01-kkr009.m4a",
      "text": "あの人だったら、どう踊るのかな？\nって、考えながらやってるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I do something‚ I ask myself‚\n“What would she do? How would she dance?”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "あの人……？\n莉央さんか葵のことか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Who?\nRio-san? Aoi?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_01-kkr010.m4a",
      "text": "ぶぶ～っ。お二人は確かに尊敬してますけど\n今は別の方を解析中ですぅ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nope! I respect both of them‚ of course‚\nbut I’m studying someone else at the moment.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "へぇ、こころが莉央さんと葵以外に？\n誰なんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You are? Someone other than Rio-san or Aoi?\nWho is it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.73333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_01-kkr011.m4a",
      "text": "それは個人情報なので秘密――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That is highly sensitive personal information—",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ぐ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "*rumble*",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.4,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_hungry-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 103.4
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_01-kkr012.m4a",
      "text": "――なのですが、美味しいご飯を食べれば\nつい、口走ってしまう可能性はありますね～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—but I might be persuaded to spill the beans\nif I was treated to something delicious to eat.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "……ファミレスでも、行くか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…How about I take you to a family restaurant?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires",
      "startTime": 119.43333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires",
      "startTime": 119.43333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_01-kkr013.m4a",
      "text": "ごちそうさまでした！\nでは、私はレッスンに戻るので、これで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks for the meal!\nTime to get back to my lessons!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires",
      "startTime": 125.466666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "待て待て！　食べてばっかりで\nまだ何も話をしてないだろう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hold on! All you did was eat.\nYou haven’t told me anything yet.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.33333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires",
      "startTime": 130.03333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_01-kkr014.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ～、そうでした。えっと……\n{user}さんの恋愛相談ですっけ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aah‚ that’s right. Let’s see…\nAbout {user}-san's dating life‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "わざとはぐらかしてるだろ\n今、こころが研究してるアイドルのことだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Stop trying to avoid the subject.\nI want to know about the idol you’re studying.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires",
      "startTime": 141.96666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_01-kkr015.m4a",
      "text": "ここはあえて聞かない方が男らしくて\nこころはカッコいいと思うんですけど～？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think it would be a lot cooler and like a real man\nif you just didn’t ask anything else.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "カッコ悪くて結構だ。マネージャーの職務として\nアイドルが考えていることは、把握しておきたいんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don’t care about being cool. As your manager‚\nI need to understand what you’re thinking.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.73333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires",
      "startTime": 155.03333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_01-kkr016.m4a",
      "text": "仕方ないですね～\nそこまで言うなら教えてあげましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ fine!\nI’ll tell you since you insist.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.33333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires",
      "startTime": 160.26666666666668
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
